{"tid":1514764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"CNN引用「造假」片 向警方道歉","createTime":"2019-08-29T01:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T07:27:21.000Z","uid":187876,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0c72091fa501ac43765a263c87e38fd03582ee87","tid":1514764,"uid":187876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:16:00.000Z","msg":"在上周日的荃灣衝突中，激進示威者投擲多個汽油彈，但翌日網上流傳一段短片，片中懷疑有汽油彈從警員方向擲出；連美國媒體CNN亦「中招」，引用了該短片，事後要去信向警方道歉。<br />\n<br />\nCNN的道歉信指，就上周日晚在CNN的新聞平台上出現一條題為「警察用汽油彈及水炮車對付香港示威者」的新聞，有關報道不實。CNN已就此進行調查，希望查出發生此錯誤的原因。CNN強調，該公司致力確保所有有關香港示威的報道是真確及平衡，因此對於發生此錯誤致歉。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科高級警司（媒體聯絡及傳訊）江永祥昨天亦表示，留意到有片段在網上流傳，指有汽油彈從警方防線擲向示威者，他澄清指，相關片段是有人惡意刪改的片段。他說，若有人透過刪改片段以掩飾暴徒惡行，是不能成功的。他又說，有外國媒體錯誤報道警方向示威者使用汽油彈，媒體已澄清，並向警方致歉。<br />\n<br />\n另外，《環球時報》報道，香港警隊部分成員包括近日有份處理反修例示威暴亂的受傷警察，獲邀在十．一期間前往北京參加國慶慶典相關活動。據悉，有機會赴京參與慶典活動的警察人數約有十人，當中在七月三十日晚暴徒圍堵葵涌警署時負傷的「光頭警長」劉Sir亦有份。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1578919/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%8D%83%E8%91%B5%E9%9D%92%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-CNN%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8-%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87-%E7%89%87-%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1578919%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E8%258D%2583%25E8%2591%25B5%25E9%259D%2592%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-CNN%25E5%25BC%2595%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%2581%2587-%25E7%2589%2587-%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AD%2589&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTLXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=1b0066d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1578919%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E8%258D%2583%25E8%2591%25B5%25E9%259D%2592%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-CNN%25E5%25BC%2595%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%2581%2587-%25E7%2589%2587-%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%2581%2593%25E6%25AD%2589&h=183744e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1578919/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%8D%83%E8%91%B5%E9%9D%92%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-CNN%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8-%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87-%E7%89%87-%E5%90%91%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89</a>"},{"pid":"33382aa8d871792f7b8a7f973bd34638d60ac160","tid":1514764,"uid":257622,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:18:20.000Z","msg":"咪撚再玩假新聞"},{"pid":"b599f70f8971395b5444bab3f14e0c4f42a21943","tid":1514764,"uid":210031,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:20:40.000Z","msg":"警世post 唔好再話fake new對自己人有用，有用嘅情況只喺對家屋企做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，成班on99"},{"pid":"c1f3b9cc8f8af47d8b09f8e08a581df67a9d0c42","tid":1514764,"uid":187876,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"以後仲有冇外煤信?"},{"pid":"e446cdadb1582d3aafd15a14965f34919e3ff7b1","tid":1514764,"uid":140326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:22:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">借呢樣嘢SPIN去人民日報啦<br />\n老屈跪地男掉磚</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3dab8922684b2594d8e05d4c9ec7204057e213a5","tid":1514764,"uid":108347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:22:56.000Z","msg":"雖然cnn假開但係而家我地需要佢，唔好推走佢地"},{"pid":"c34a557a105396fb8e29ec3f460c01509dfc13ca","tid":1514764,"uid":215876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:23:56.000Z","msg":"咪再推fake news"},{"pid":"30a2661f2ac6c78dbbcb87ae50717d119abd2312","tid":1514764,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e446cdadb1582d3aafd15a14965f34919e3ff7b1","tid":1514764,"uid":140326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:22:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">借呢樣嘢SPIN去人民日報啦<br />\n老屈跪地男掉磚</span></strong></span>"},"